column10: There is no sidewalk and no street lights. One one hand people are being encouraged to use public transportation and on other hand this is risky because no sidewalk and once it is dark, then no light.
column21: this is not an incident, just informing the lack of sidewalk and lack of street lights. There is a bus stop at Lake Newport Road / Arbor Glen, but there is no sidewalk to Autumn Ridge. Crossing the road in pitch dark risky. There are no street lights from Lake Newport Road / Arbon Glen to Autumn Ridge Circle, Woodcrest Dr or Twisted Oak Dr
